result.name: Novel lncRNA lncFAM200B: molecular characteristics and effects of genetic variants on promoter activity and cattle body measurement traits
result.description: According to the RNA-Seq data, a novel lncRNA (named as lncFAM200B) was identified in cattle, and its promoter active region was proved. Then a single nucleotide polymorphism (SNP) was uncovered in the promoter active rigion.
result.center: College of Animal Science and Technology, Northwest A&F University
